Package dataStructure

Class node

java.lang.Object
dataStructure.node
All Implemented Interfaces:
node_data, java.io.Serializable
public class node
extends java.lang.Object
implements node_data, java.io.Serializable
This interface represents the set of operations applicable on a node (vertex) in a (directional) positive weighted graph.
Author:
Dolev Brender, Avihai Bernholtz
